<HEADLINE> Tunis Stock Exchange Index Closes Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TUNIS, April 7 (Xinhua) -- The Tunis Stock Exchange index
closed at 567.67 points Wednesday, down 0.29 percent from Tuesday's
finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 102,352 shares changed hands in 324 deals,
with the turnover reaching 8,051,811 dinars (7,319,828 U.S.
dollars). 
</P>
