Pakistan's endeavors in this regard.
</P>
<P>
While reviewing the Middle East situation, the two leaders
shared dismay at the impasse owing to the Israeli intransigence
and hoped that the international community will exercise vigilance
and make concerted action in order to push the peace process
forward.
