<HEADLINE> Iraq Urges Security Council to Stop U.S., British  Aggression </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, April 7 (Xinhua) -- Iraq called on the United
Nations Security Council to take a clear and unambiguous position
on the U.S. and British aggression.
</P>
