<HEADLINE> Mugabe Leaves For Angola </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, April 7 (Xinhua) -- Zimbabwean President Robert Mugabe
left here for Luanda on Wednesday afternoon for a summit of
Southern African Development Community (SADC) allied forces
involved in the war in Congo (K), the Zimbabwe's Foreign Ministry
said in a statement.
</P>
