<HEADLINE> GA Decides to Open Fifty-fourth Session on </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, April 8 (Xinhua) -- The United Nations General
Assembly (GA) had decided to open its fifty-fourth session on
September 14, 1999, U.N. sources said here on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
According to the sources, the current session of the General
Assembly will close on September 13, 1999.
</P>
<P>
The general debate of the fifty-fourth session will be held
from September 20 to 25 and from September 29 to October 2, 1999.
</P>
<P>
